- **Add a section on the formal mathematical/statistical foundation of power**, including formulas for power calculation in hypothesis testing and sample size estimation with illustrative examples.
- **Incorporate discipline-specific typical power statistics and meta-analysis findings** to contextualize why statistical power matters broadly and highlight common power deficiencies.
- **Introduce content on Bayesian power concepts and the controversy around post hoc power analysis**, to cover advanced statistical considerations.
- **Develop or embed interactive power visualizations or animations** similar to competitors’ tools to enhance user engagement and education.

### 🟡 MEDIUM IMPACT (Opportunity Gaps)
