- **Expand discussion on experimental design factors beyond sample size affecting power**, such as measurement precision, variance reduction, and design efficiency (e.g., blocking).
- **Add intuitive analogies linking statistical power to test sensitivity and clinical diagnostics**, especially relevant for clinical/medical readers.

### 🟢 LOW IMPACT (Differentiators)
